@startuml
skinparam participantBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam lifelineStrategy solid

actor "Quản trị viên" as User #Yellow
boundary "RegistrationsPage" as UI #Yellow
boundary "AxiosClient" as API #Yellow
control "JwtMiddleware" as MW #Yellow
control "BookingsController" as Ctrl #Yellow
control "BookingService" as Svc #Yellow
entity "Booking" as BEnt #Yellow
entity "Customer" as CEnt #Yellow
entity "Tour" as TEnt #Yellow
database "PostgreSQL" as DB #Yellow

User -> UI : 1: Mở trang quản lý đăng ký
activate UI
UI -> UI : 1.1: TanStack Query gọi\ngetAll với status filter
UI -> API : 1.2: GET /api/Bookings\nHeader: Authorization: Bearer {token}\n?Status=0&PageSize=20
activate API

API -> API : 1.3: Axios interceptor: gắn Bearer token
API -> MW : 1.4: Request qua JwtMiddleware
activate MW
MW -> MW : 1.5: ValidateToken
alt 1.6: [Token không hợp lệ]
MW --> API : 1.6.1: 401
API --> UI : 1.6.2: Redirect login
else 1.7: [Token hợp lệ]
MW --> Ctrl : 1.7.1: Chuyển tiếp
deactivate MW

activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Ctrl : 1.8: Bind query params -> BookingFilterRequest
Ctrl -> Svc : 1.9: GetAllAsync(filter)
activate Svc

Svc -> DB : 1.10: Bookings.GetQueryable()\n.Include(b => b.Customer)\n.Include(b => b.Tour)
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 1.10.1: IQueryable<Booking>
deactivate DB

alt 1.11: [BookingCode không rỗng]
Svc -> Svc : 1.11.1: query.Where(b => b.BookingCode.Contains(code))
else 1.12: [CustomerId.HasValue]
Svc -> Svc : 1.12.1: query.Where(b => b.CustomerId == value)
else 1.13: [TourId.HasValue]
Svc -> Svc : 1.13.1: query.Where(b => b.TourId == value)
else 1.14: [Status.HasValue]
Svc -> Svc : 1.14.1: query.Where(b => b.Status == value)
else 1.15: [StartDate.HasValue]
Svc -> Svc : 1.15.1: query.Where(b => b.StartDate >= value)
else 1.16: [EndDate.HasValue]
Svc -> Svc : 1.16.1: query.Where(b => b.StartDate <= value)
end

Svc -> DB : 1.17: query.CountAsync()
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 1.17.1: total
deactivate DB

Svc -> DB : 1.18: query.OrderByDescending(b => b.CreatedAt)\n.Skip((page-1)*pageSize).Take(pageSize)\n.ToListAsync()
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 1.18.1: List<Booking> (có Customer, Tour)
deactivate DB

Svc -> Svc : 1.19: _mapper.Map<List<BookingResponse>>(items)\n(Mapping: CustomerName, TourName)
Svc -> Svc : 1.20: Tạo PagedResult<BookingResponse>
Svc --> Ctrl : 1.21: ApiResponse.Ok(PagedResult)
deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> API : 1.22: 200 OK
deactivate Ctrl
API --> UI : 1.23: Response JSON (danh sách booking)
deactivate API

UI -> UI : 1.24: Hiển thị bảng booking\n(mã, khách hàng, tour, ngày, trạng thái,\nhành động)
UI --> User : 1.25: Xem danh sách đăng ký
deactivate UI

@enduml
